  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t祈使句的反意疑问句</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t1．祈使句的反意疑问部分为肯定形式,要用shall,will.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Pass me the book,will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t2．Let&rsquo;s表示第一人称的祈使句,反意疑问句为&ldquo;Shall we?&rdquo;.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Let&rsquo;s go for a walk,shall we?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Let&rsquo;s forget it,shall we?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t3．Let me和Let us 表示第二人称的祈使句,反意疑问句为&ldquo;will you?&rdquo;.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Let us go for a walk,will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t4．其它行为动词引起的祈使句,无论其陈述部分是否定还是肯定的祈使句,多用&ldquo;will you?&rdquo;,表一种客气的语气.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Listen to me,will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Don&rsquo;t tell anyone about it,will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t但在肯定的祈使句后有时也用&ldquo;won&rsquo;t you?&rdquo;表&ldquo;提醒对方注意&rdquo;或表&ldquo;邀请&rdquo;.如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Have a cup of coffee,won&rsquo;t you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Come in and take a seat,won&rsquo;t you／will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t祈使句用于两个重要句型中</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t1．<strong><span style=\"color: #f00;\">&ldquo;祈使句+and+表结果的陈述句&rdquo;用来叙述肯定的条件.</span></strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t2．<strong><span style=\"color: #f00;\">&ldquo;祈使句+or(else)+表结果的陈述句&rdquo;用来叙述否定的条件,or(else)表示&ldquo;否则；要不然&rdquo;.试比较：</span></strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hurry up and you&rsquo;ll catch the train.(＝If you hurry up,you&rsquo;ll catch the train．)</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hurry up,or you&rsquo;ll miss the train．(＝If you don&rsquo;t hurry up,you&rsquo;ll miss the train．)</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">祈使句由直接引语变成间接引语</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #f00;\">当祈使句由直接引语变成间接引语时,其常用结构为&ldquo;ask／request／tell／order sb(not)to do sth&rdquo;.</span></strong></div>\n<div>\n\t如：<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo;Speak loudly,please!&rdquo; the teacher said to me．(＝The teacher asked me to speak loudly．)</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t smoke in the meeting room!&rdquo; he said to Tom．(＝He told Tom not to smoke in the meeting room．)</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772473/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772473\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772215/\">纪录片《我们女王90岁》：凯特王妃领衔爆料</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772256/\">福原爱要嫁台北小伙?!东北腔要被台湾腔带跑</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772114/\">7幅漫画概括现代女性的纠结 我怎么都躺枪了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772324/\">到底有没有the？这是一个值得思考的问题</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772157/\">我们男神都有“绅士手”！绅士手英文怎么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771946/\">英语里表达“也许”的15种方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771876/\">致有梦想的你：如何成为生活的赢家？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772264/\">这只三条腿军犬的故事 感动了全世界……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772298/\">英18岁情侣因战乱分离 72年后重逢前缘再续</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772398/\">刷爆Instagram的父女插画 爸比是我的守护神</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
