  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t祈使句后也可以加简略问句，表示语气。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; 否定祈使句+will you?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; 肯定祈使句+won&rsquo;t you?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; 肯定祈使句+will you?（表示请求）&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Let&rsquo;s &hellip; + shall we?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Let us &hellip; + will you?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Let +第三人称&hellip;&hellip;+ will you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t注：let us与let&rsquo;s的区别：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t（1）let us do sth. 让(或允许)我们做某事；即提出请求，请对方允许，而对方不做，只有我们做。附加疑问句用will you?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如：Let us have a rest, will you? 让我们休息一下，好吗？</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t（2）let&rsquo;s do sth. 咱们去做某事吧；即提出建议，劝诱对方一同做某事，附加疑问句用shall we?&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如：Let&rsquo;s go for a picnic, shall we? 咱们去野餐吧，好吗？</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>总结祈使句的用法<br />\n\t</strong></span></div>\n<div>\n\t祈使句所能表达的含义：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t命令：Make your bed at once! 马上把床铺好！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t禁止：Don&rsquo;t touch! 不要碰！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t请求，恳求：Shut the door, please. 请关门。 Help! 救命！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t忠告，劝告：Lock the door before you go to bed. 睡觉前把门锁上。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t建议，指示：Let&rsquo;s have a party! 咱们举行个聚会吧。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Take the first street on the left.走右边第一条街。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t邀请：Make yourself at home! 请自便（别客气）</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Come in and sit down. 进来坐。&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Help yourself to some fruit. 吃点水果。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t提供：Have some orange juice. 喝点橙汁吧。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t祝愿：Have a good time! 祝你（过得）愉快！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t警告，威胁：Look out! 当心！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Do that again and you will be in trouble! 你在那样做会倒霉的！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t允诺：Finish your homework and I&rsquo;ll buy you some food.做完作业就给你买吃的。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t诅咒：Go to hell! 滚！</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t自忖：Let me see now. 让我考虑考虑。</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772470/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772470\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772215/\">纪录片《我们女王90岁》：凯特王妃领衔爆料</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772256/\">福原爱要嫁台北小伙?!东北腔要被台湾腔带跑</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772114/\">7幅漫画概括现代女性的纠结 我怎么都躺枪了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772324/\">到底有没有the？这是一个值得思考的问题</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772157/\">我们男神都有“绅士手”！绅士手英文怎么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771946/\">英语里表达“也许”的15种方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771876/\">致有梦想的你：如何成为生活的赢家？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772264/\">这只三条腿军犬的故事 感动了全世界……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772298/\">英18岁情侣因战乱分离 72年后重逢前缘再续</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772398/\">刷爆Instagram的父女插画 爸比是我的守护神</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
